We have fitted all three graphs with equivalent circuit shown in Fig. 10
                     a and b with the parameters' value. It has been observed that the carbon supports significantly reduced the charge transfer resistance (R ct). Also, we know that catalytic activity is inversely proportional to the R ct [77]. The value of R ct in S,N-GQD/TiO2/C-800 (35 Ω) is lower than S,N-GQD/TiO2 (500 Ω), and S,N-GQD/TiO2/C (38 Ω) (Table 3
                     ).
